Sb/Esb/Sbm/Esbm - guild chatlines
------------------------------------------------------------
The guild chat lines. The sb line is the main channel, heard
by all members; esb emotes over it. Sbm and esbm are the
Blademaster channels, which can be used (and heard) only by
Blademasters (GL 15).

GL:  1 (sb) or 15 (sbm)
SP:  0
command:  sb/esb/sbm/esbm <text>, sbhist sbmhist
duration: N/A
